<div class="title">Amphetamine Addiction</div>
<div class="substance">Amphetamines (Adderall) & Methylphenidate</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Bishop+Knight&Exact=1">Bishop Knight</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Bishop Knight. "Amphetamine Addiction: An Experience with Amphetamines (Adderall) & Methylphenidate (exp983)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Sep 8, 2000. erowid.org/exp/983</div>

<br/>



